<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sorry we missed you!</title>
</head>

<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f3f4f6; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#374151;">

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f3f4f6; padding:24px;">
<tr>
<td align="center">

<table role="presentation" width="600" style="background:#ffffff; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:8px;">

  <!-- Body -->
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:30px 24px 0 24px; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#374151;">

      <p style="margin:0; padding:0px 0 0 0;">
        Hi <strong>{{ client_name|default('Valued Customer') }}</strong>,
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0; padding:20px 0 0 0;">
        We note that we were unable to connect for our scheduled consultation earlier today.
        We understand that calendars can fluctuate, and we remain ready to assist you whenever you are prepared to resume.
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0; padding:20px 0 0 0;">
        In the meantime, feel free to explore our latest workspace designs and furniture applications in our <a href="{{ project_link|default('#') }}"> Featured Projects </a> collection for layout inspiration.
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0; padding:20px 0 0 0;">
        When you are ready to secure an alternative time slot, you can easily schedule a new session using the link below:
      </p>

    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="padding:20px;">
      <a href="{{ booking_link|default('#') }}"
         style="background:#255793; color:#ffffff; padding:12px 24px; text-decoration:none; border-radius:6px; display:inline-block;">
        Reschedule Consultation
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:0 24px 20px; font-size:16px; line-height:24px; color:#374151;">

      <p style="margin:0;">
        Alternatively, if you have any immediate questions regarding our product ranges or showroom locations, please feel free to reply directly to this email.
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0; padding:20px 0 0 0;">
        Best regards,
      </p>

      <p style="margin:0; padding:20px 0 0 0;">
        <strong>{{ sender_name|default('Krost Sales Team') }}</strong>
      </p>

    </td>
  </tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>